title: The Best Advice of 2020
description:
Sadie shares the amazing advice that brought the house down in 2020, featuring Christine Caine, Kari Jobe, Max Lucado, Lauren Daigle, Mike and Natalie Todd, Jennie Allen, Miles Fidell, and some familiar faces from Sadie's family: John Luke Robertson, Bella Robertson, Willie Robertson, and Chrys Howard (aka 2-mama). These quotes are so quotable you'll be repeating them for years to come.
